Introduction

Lingling is a Malaysian trainee under LeanBranding. She is a member of the upcoming girl group KIIRAS.

In 2024, she was a contestant on Mnet's survival show I-LAND2: N/a, where she was sadly eliminated in episode 7. At that time, she was a trainee under WAKEONE.
